# Simple React Example

```jsx
function App() {
    return (
        <h1>Hello React!</h1>
    );
}

export default App;
```

### Explanation

* `function App()` defines a React component.
* `return` specifies what should appear on the screen.
* `<h1>Hello React!</h1>` is JSX.
* `export default App;` makes the component available to other files.

